Former DE 404 Alternate
Delaware Route&nbsp;404 Alternate (DE&nbsp;404 Alt.) was a  alternate route of DE&nbsp;404 that bypassed the town of Bridgeville. It ran to the north of Bridgeville on Newton Road and to the east of Bridgeville on US&nbsp;13. The route was created by 1990. The alignment of DE&nbsp;404 Alt. was replaced by DE&nbsp;404 in 1999. The route of DE&nbsp;404 in Bridgeville then became known as DE&nbsp;404 Bus.
